	   <form action=http://www1.allakhazam.com/perl/strategy/mrate.pl name=f9856751447033><tr><td id=headerrow><span id=sj>RE: Need help to learn a good technique for a level 12 ENC</span></td><td align=right id=headerrow valign=bottom><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=16821><span id=Scholar>Fiddo</span></a>, <span id=Scholar>Scholar</span><br><span id=notbold>536 posts</td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 id=headerrow>Posted @ Tue, Mar 27th 1:39 AM 2001</td>
	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Decent<span id=notbold>[3.42]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>Ok sounds good to me, cept ye should cast tashan as the first spell ye cast, if nothing else to get ye into the habit, plus ye get much much less resists, as to yer lvl, 12 is the lvl where I found that finally groups were more willing to take me in, not as willing as at 16 with me breeze but was good.<br><br>In the early lvls me enchanter did exactly as ye doing, blasting and using pet then at 12 started grouping to do crocs in oasis, with yer new buffs and stuff tis easy to get group, at 16th I went to Lake Of Ill Omen and havent looked back yet.<br><br>Fear is a good tecknique but ye need to partner with a druid or necro to cast darkness or snare to slow crit down, with a good partner specially necro its almost silly how easy it is to reverse kite crits while yer pets bang on them.:P<br><br>As far as later with groups, the first thing youll be casting is yer tash series as it will help yer other casters, mostly when grouped so far I hardly cast any offensive spells, mostly my mana is used on the various buffs, and crowd control spells. and I dont use pets when in group because if my mez failes on one or two of the crits they aggro me and me pet attacks and makes it so Im unable to recast mezz.<br><br>Only 10 deaths? sounds good to me, dont want to relate how many Ive died..more times than I care to say. Enchanters dieing is a common thing ye wiol get used to it, often because mezz is a big aggro factor and ye dont always find the best group ,youll be the only one to die,:P oh well tis only a game, dust yer self off and get back in there mate:)<br>&nbsp;<br>Fiddo Lupineopolus<br>Cazic Thule<br>What do you mean being lazy is no way to live? It's the only thing I'm good at.</td></tr>
